        <h2>Welcome to Arkansas Citizens Action</h2>
        <p>
            Arkansas Citizens Action is a grassroots initiative aimed at providing Arkansans with the tools and information 
            needed to contact their representatives and advocate for important issues. Below are some key topics you can explore.
        </p>
        
        <h3>How to Use This Site</h3>
        <p>
            Click on any topic in the navigation bar to learn more. Each page contains information about the issue, 
            relevant legislation, and how you can take action by contacting your state representatives.
        </p>
        
